1) Basic posting
================
User can visit dashboard where all posts are displayed in order
User can make a text post, which will then appear on the page next time it refreshes
User can delete a post
Dashboard should contain 20 posts, then fetch more as the user scrolls to the bottom


2) Accounts
===========
User can create account
User can log in to account
User can log out
User can delete account
User can follow and unfollow other accounts by typing their name exactly
    this includes federated accounts
User should see posts only associated with the people they follow
Users posts should be sent out to other people (federated)


3) ???????
==========


?) Polishing
============
Loading gif or message should appear at the bottom when the user scrolls,
    or "no more posts" if there are no more to display
